LFI Attack is Local File Inclusion Attack. It's mainly talking about how to use local file on server to do further attack, contains disclose sensitive info
or RCE.

RFI is Remote File Inclusion Attacker. It's mainly taking about how to use remote file located on itself host to do further attack.

1.LFI Attacker Form:

1-1.Uploading malicious file:
We could upload malicious file on target server.Then, do below attack:
{URL}?../../../../../{malicious file name}---->This attacker is also called "File Uploading Attack"

1-2.Log Poisoning:
